        "q": "What expenses should be included in a rental property pro forma?",
        "a": "Include property taxes, insurance, property management fees, repairs and maintenance, landlord-paid utilities, landscaping, and a capital expenditure reserve for major replacements. A common mistake is omitting the CapEx reserve and management fee, both of which can swing your NOI by several percentage points."
